        <updateDate>2011-11-09T20:38:44Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Federal Employees Leave Transfer Act of 2011 - Directs the Office of Personnel Management (OPM) to modify by regulation the program for voluntary transfer of unused leave to allow federal employees to transfer unused sick leave and contribute such leave to agency leave banks for the use of other employees, on the same basis as is allowed for annual leave. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
